               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3r-143v)&#xD; -
                     Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 3ra l.1–7rb l.26)&#xD; - Maṣḥaf
                     za-wäḍʾat ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “The Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 10vb
                     l.17–17rb l.7)&#xD; - Lǝfāfa ṣǝdǝq “Bandlet of Righteousness”, followed by
                     Ṣalota mangada samāy “Prayer of the Journey to Heaven” (fols. 19ra l.15–23rb
                     l.21)&#xD; - Homily of ʾAbbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 90vb
                     l.7–93ra l.1)&#xD; - Maṣḥafa ʾardǝʾt “Book of the Disciples” (fols. 124vb
                     l.11–126vb l.2)&#xD; - Antiphons from Mawāśǝʾt (fols. 132ra l.1–133vb
                     l.23)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-2.</summary>
